---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import WebhookManager from '../components/WebhookManager';
import WebhookAnalyticsDashboard from '../components/WebhookAnalyticsDashboard';

// Check if user is authenticated
const user = Astro.locals.user;
if (!user) {
  return Astro.redirect('/giris');
}

// Get auth token from session
const authToken = Astro.cookies.get('auth-token')?.value || '';
---

<Layout title="Webhooks">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <div class="mb-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Webhooks</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Uygulamalarınızı gerçek zamanlı olaylarla entegre edin</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100 rounded-lg p-6 border border-blue-200">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-900">Webhook Nedir?</h3>
          <span class="text-2xl">🔗</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-blue-800">
          Webhooks, belirli olaylar gerçekleştiğinde URL'nize HTTP POST istekleri göndererek sisteminizi güncellenmiş tutar.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-green-100 rounded-lg p-6 border border-green-200">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-900">Güvenlik</h3>
          <span class="text-2xl">🔒</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-green-800">
          Tüm webhook istekleri HMAC-SHA256 imzası ile doğrulanır. X-Signature başlığında bulunur.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-purple-100 rounded-lg p-6 border border-purple-200">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-purple-900">Otomatik Yeniden Deneme</h3>
          <span class="text-2xl">🔄</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-purple-800">
          Başarısız teslimler otomatik olarak katlanarak artan gecikmelerle yeniden denenilir.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Webhook Manager -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 mb-8">
      <WebhookManager client:load userId={user.id} token={authToken} />
    </div>

    <!-- Webhook Analytics Dashboard -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 mb-8">
      <WebhookAnalyticsDashboard client:load token={authToken} />
    </div>

    <!-- Documentation -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Başlangıç Rehberi</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">1️⃣ Webhook Oluşturun</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">
            Yukarıdaki "Yeni Webhook" butonuna tıklayarak yeni webhook oluşturun.
            Olay türü, URL ve (isteğe bağlı) secret sağlayın.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded p-3 text-sm font-mono">
            Event: place.created<br/>
            URL: https://yourapp.com/webhooks/places<br/>
            Secret: your-secret-key
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">2️⃣ İmzayı Doğrulayın</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">
            Her webhook isteği X-Signature başlığında HMAC-SHA256 imzası ile gelir.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded p-3 text-sm font-mono overflow-x-auto">
            const crypto = require('crypto');<br/>
            const signature = crypto<br/>
            &nbsp;&nbsp;.createHmac('sha256', secret)<br/>
            &nbsp;&nbsp;.update(JSON.stringify(body))<br/>
            &nbsp;&nbsp;.digest('hex');
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">3️⃣ Test Edin</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Webhook listesinden webhook seçerek "Test Et" butonuyla örnek olay gönderin.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">4️⃣ İzleyin</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            "Analitikler" sekmesinden webhook teslim oranını, başarısız olayları ve performans metriklerini izleyin.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border border-blue-200">
        <p class="text-sm text-blue-800">
          <strong>💡 İpucu:</strong> Webhook URL'niz geçerli bir HTTPS adresi olmalı ve 200-299 arasında HTTP durum kodu döndürmelidir.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
